      "value": "<p><b>Source</b> <em>Ultimate Equipment pg. 21</em>, <em>Ultimate Combat pg. 132</em></p><h3><span title=\"PFS Legal\">[PFS]</span> Statistics</h3><p><b>Cost</b> 6 gp <b>Weight</b> 1 lb.</p><p><b>Damage</b> 1d3 (small), 1d4 (medium); <b>Critical</b> x2; <b>Range</b> 20 ft.; <b>Type</b> S or P; <b>Special</b> disarm, grapple, monk, reach</p><p><b>Category</b> Two-Handed; <b>Proficiency</b> Exotic</p><p><b>Weapon Groups</b> Flails; Monk</p><h3>Description</h3><p>This weapon consists of a foot-long double-edged blade, with another smaller, curved hook-blade sticking out the side like a rooster's spur. The blade is strung to a large iron hoop with a 10-foot length of rope. The blade can be used as an off-handed melee weapon or thrown like a dagger, while the rope and circlet can be whipped around and swung at opponents as a bludgeoning reach weapon.</p>"
